<plot>"Acting Like a Thief" is a short film about the Budhan Theatre of Chharanagar. Starting with playwright Dakxin Bajrange discussing his arrest the film brings us inside the lives of a dedicated group of young actors and their families as they discuss what it means to be a "born criminal"; and how theater changed their lives.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?022764</url></doc>
